review: She is not a doctor. She is like mother to me , when i met her with lots of fear n tension that i got from my previous hospital experience, they recommend operation for my medical problem. tags: Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,Doctor friendliness,
review: We visited this hospital for periods issue. Instead of discussing the issue, as soon as we entered the room, she said that my sister has turner syndrome ***** **** ** *** ******* **** **** **** ** *** ** ***** ** *****. She has come to a conclusion about the  problem *** ****** *** *** ***** **** ******* ********* ** *** ******** Used some technical terms and telling that my sister has some serious problem. She prescribed scan and urine test. Very strangely she don't have time to write the report details about the scan and when we ask them repeatedly about the reports continuously for two days she sent a report ***** ******* **** ******* ******. And there is no lab technician signature also on the report. **** *** ***** ****** ****** **** ******** I humbly request people not to go to this hospital for gynic issues. **** *** **** ********* ***** ***** *** ************* **** **** **** **** * **** **** ******* ***** *** ******* *********** ****** *** **** *** ****** **** *** ** ***** *** **** **** ** ***** ********** *** *******. It is minimum responsibility to share the reports for which they have charged. For that also we called them several times to get the reports. After seeing the reports, we felt that reports are being prepared and not actual reports. Please don't visit this hospital. We went to this hospital based on Google reviews ***** **** ** ** ********** *** ******* .They are constructing a new building in kphb , don't trust the hospital and this doctor. *** **** ***** ***** *** **** *** **** **** ******* ******* *** **** ****** **** ***** ***** *** ****** *** *** **** *** *** *** *********

tags: Doctor friendliness,Treatment satisfaction,Explanation of the health issue,
context: Female Infertility Treatment,PCOD/PCOS Treatment,Diagnosis of unexplained infertility,
review:
We have initially consulted Dr. Sree Gowri in 2018 based on friend suggestion. Took initial treatment. Since the hospital was far from our home, we have decided to go to nearby hospital as we thought our problem was not special. Visited all major hospitals for one year and came back to madam, since nobody could understand our problem. We wasted one year in meantime.
We came back to consultation with Dr. Gowri in 2019 December. Started treatment. Undergone lap surgery here. We could see improvement in our results. Now conceived in June. 

Madam answers any question related to infertility. The experience in the field of infertility is vast with the doctor here.
